Portions of the RAG pipeline — the document chunker, retriever, system-prompt
skeleton, and the ingest file-walking/batching layout — are derived from:

  rootsongjc/rag-chatbot  (https://github.com/rootsongjc/rag-chatbot)
  Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

  You may obtain a copy of the Apache License at:
  http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0

Those parts have been substantially adapted: the embedding and generation
providers were replaced with Cloudflare Workers AI for embeddings and
Anthropic Claude via Cloudflare AI Gateway for chat, bilingual logic was
removed, the prompt/branding was made configuration-driven, and a new
embeddable widget UI was added. See the upstream repository for its original
NOTICE and license terms.
